Read `.devlyn/surface-close.input.patch` and the current contents of `server/index.js` and `tests/server.test.js`. Evaluate the UVR-STALE and PATH-TEST obligations above against the Goal. Make the smallest sufficient edit (or none) within `authorized_surface`, then reply with the two required obligation lines followed by `PASS` or `BLOCKED:surface-close-<reason>`.
